    P53   General Merchandise Stores.
    P54   Food Stores.
    P55   Automotive Dealers and Service Stations.
    P56   Apparel and Accessory Stores.
    P57   Furniture and Homefurnishings Stores.
    P59   Miscellaneous Retail.
</IN>
