fourth quarter.
Sales in the quarter rose 16 per cent to Dollars 2.5bn, from Dollars 2.2bn.
Of that, Dollars 515m was outside North America. For the year, Deere posted
net income of Dollars 603.6m, Dollars 7.01 a share, up from Dollars 248m, or
Dollars 3.21, before special charges.
