FT  07 DEC 94 / Glaxo sued for Pounds 80m by patients
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
   By RICHARD WOLFFE
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
Glaxo, the pharmaceuticals manufacturer, is being sued for more than Pounds
